## Log 1: vCenter Service Failure (503 Error)

### Timestamp
2026-05-06 10:15:32

### Issue
vCenter Server UI not accessible (HTTP 503 Service Unavailable)

### Observed Symptoms
- Web client not responding
- ESXi hosts still reachable via direct client
- vCenter services not loading

### Root Cause Analysis
vCenter services were not fully initialized after reboot.

### Resolution Steps
- Connected via SSH to VCSA
- Checked service status
- Restarted all services

### Result
vCenter UI restored successfully at 10:22

