## Log 2: iSCSI Datastore Not Visible

### Timestamp
2026-05-06 11:05:10

### Issue
Shared datastore not visible on ESXi Host 2 (192.168.4.20)

### Observed Symptoms
- Datastore missing in storage view
- VM migration failed
- Path to LUN unavailable

### Root Cause Analysis
Storage adapter not rescanned after network configuration change.

### Resolution Steps
- Performed rescan of storage adapters
- Verified connectivity to storage network
- Re-registered iSCSI target

### Result
Datastore successfully mounted on both ESXi hosts

