## Log 3: VM Network Isolation Issue

### Timestamp
2026-05-06 12:30:44

### Issue
VM02 unable to communicate with other VMs

### Observed Symptoms
- Ping failure between VM02 and VM03
- No external connectivity issues

### Root Cause Analysis
Incorrect port group assignment in virtual switch configuration

### Resolution Steps
- Verified port group settings in vSphere
- Reassigned VM NIC to correct network
- Restarted network interface

### Result
Network connectivity restored

